Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The furthest space city from Earth,\Nknown as Side 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...proclaimed itself the Principality of Z eon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In roughly one month of fighting,\Nthe Principality of Z eon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Federation Forces caused\Nthe deaths of half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape From Luna II
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Madagascar, locked onto beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Docking speed, maximum minus 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitude, steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Madagascar, entering port.\NDocking crews, prepare to secure the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons loaders, on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Recreation services, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to receive our troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pier Number 2, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondary combat equipment will be loaded\Nas soon as Madagascar is docked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have over 100 civilians with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They had no choice but to leave Side 7\Nwhen it was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to take them if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But the base at Luna II has been in\Na constant state of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally arrive at a friendly base\Nand we can't even rest? How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Wakkein,\NCommandant of the Luna II forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Bright Noa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The refugees are exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to find them somewhere to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been pursued by the Z eons,\Nso there's been no time for resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot accommodate civilians here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, please remain where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After we consult with\NFederation Forces HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...you will be sent to Earth immediately\Non a suitable ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- To Earth?!\N- We want to go back to Side 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be separating the following\Nfrom the regular refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright Noa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai Yashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu Jose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla Mass...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai Shiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato Kobayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's your problem? Leave them alone!\N- Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us an explanation, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadets and civilians have taken control\Nof Triple-A classified technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...namely, the White Base and the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you can expect to face\Na military court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base shall be seized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam shall be secured and\Nreturned to military control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- That is all.\N- That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even looked into\Nwhat happened at Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. I'm Wakkein,\NCommandant of Luna II.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of repairs to the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...also, the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You must rest well and recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with the Guntank\Nafter we secure the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll we do with it?\NIt's all in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just secure it for now.\NWakkein's pretty strict about his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A Musai will be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that Char the Red Comet\Nwill give up his pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you secure the Gundam now...\N- You're in no position to dictate our strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how dangerous\Nthe Red Comet is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're not even a regular soldier,\NI can see how you'd feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Red Comet\Nis a renowned soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't challenge Luna II\Nwith a light cruiser like the Musai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That would simply be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure Luna ll's radar can't detect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The Minovsky particle density\Nis a little low, but we should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels strange to be right in front of them,\Nyet remain undetected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that technology is so advanced...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...we're back to visual-range combat,\Njust like in the olden days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Commander,\Nshall we take out Luna II?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you're so bold, Dren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna II has extensive defense facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your average military strategist would\Nnever expect us to attack with a mere Musai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why we're going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan, Dren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that girl be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...my long-lost younger sister,\Nwhom I last saw 10 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too strong... to be Artesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drop It!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Move, and I'll shoot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NArtesia is much gentler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We will infiltrate the enemy in normal suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to capture the Federation's mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...we are to capture the enemy's new warship,\Ncodenamed Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We will only destroy them if\Nwe can't capture them. That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take me to Commandant Wakkein!\N- I think it's a waste of time, Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't guarantee\Nthat Char won't attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we can't think\Non an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta eat when you have the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you won't have energy when you need it.\NEven if you're just running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Kai Shiden says, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating meals is like\Nloading ammo into your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier's gotta eat\Neven if he doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shall we go for it, Lt. Commander?\N- Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look.\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...an infra-red security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Deploy mines without triggering the alarm.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to remember there are\Ntwo settings in the block connection lever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the biggest difference between\Nthe Gundam and Z eon's Zaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But what makes the Gundam\Nso much more superior than the Zaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike previous Zaku-type mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundam stores combat case studies\Nin its memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It stores case studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that\Nthe more the Gundam fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the more it learns\Nand the stronger it becomes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For a complete novice at piloting, like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be able to fight against\Na veteran soldier like Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It has less to do with my own skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...and more to do with the capabilities\Nof the Gundam's learning computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too humble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The centrifugal gravity system is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the power generator was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying they snuck in under our radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. We believe they're special forces\Nwearing normal suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Bright said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy the Magellan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They've probably forgotten all about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? It opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! There's no power,\Nso the electronic lock doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are Ms. Mirai and Ms. Sayla?\N- They should be in the room next to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Magellan, emergency launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the docking locks, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Z eons have begun their attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...so why haven't you evacuated us\Nto a safer location?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no orders from the Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Are you telling us\Nto stay here and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not what I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please contact the Commandant\Nand do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Commandant's busy\Nand doesn't have time to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, you brat?!\NGet over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather the crew together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving the White Base out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro, release the seals on the Gundam!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magellan is launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! It was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Magellan's blocked the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Start engines! Engineers, on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Ryu! Kai! Amuro!\N- Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you freed the Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No need to yell. We just started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla, the refugees?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're moving into the gravity block.\NFraw Bow is directing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'll go check on the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! Once the engines reach critical,\Nadvance the ship slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you injured, Commandant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's aboard the White Base?\NGet this ship alongside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you men doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I made it clear that\Nthe White Base is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the Gundam can fight against Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you to leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to be charged with treason,\NCommandant Wakkein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your enemy the Z eon forces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lecture you about\Nthe importance of military regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must obey the orders you are given!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You go on about military regulations,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care If soldiers die by those rules.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But isn't it wrong for civilians to lose lives{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wakkein...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Paolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have something to say, Wakkein...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The White Base, the Gundam,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}... were considered top secret until now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be unfortunate, but these people are\Nmore adept at using those weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They have experienced two actual battles,\Nand so we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Captain...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They are essentially amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As Commandant, you must give them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...all the support they need to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand, Captain.i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Matthew! Fix! Listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We enter the port, and take both\Nthe Trojan Horse ship and mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir!\N- Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant Wakkein.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we get rid of the Magellan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base cannot leave port.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the Luna II fleet will be\Nwiped out without a chance to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Musai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of the Magellan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure the White Base at this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All other ships take defensive positions.\NMain cannons stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower the bulkheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the Magellan's\Nthermonuclear reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, get away from the passage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of man is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's best that we leave them alone,\Nat least until they get to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Captain Paolo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the war with Z eon\Ngets more and more difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...we keep losing those people\Nwho have much to teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,These are cold times to be alive, aren't they.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rest assured we will deliver\Nyour White Base to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If a spacecraft relies on gravity alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...it will burn up during re-entry\Ninto Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Char chooses that moment\Nto attack the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Both sides face tremendous danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will they set foot upon the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-entry to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-entry to Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:54.24,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:59.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:09.46,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:14.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:19.02,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.40,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.98,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:39.29,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
